```{r ampulla 32408338, include=FALSE}

PMID_32408338 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32408338', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32408338 <- paste0(PMID_32408338$journal,' ', PMID_32408338$year, ' ', PMID_32408338$month,';', PMID_32408338$volume,'(', PMID_32408338$number,'):', PMID_32408338$pages)

PubMed_32408338 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32408338$eprint)

doi_32408338 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32408338$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
